 所以就要屌反對派同埋加入教派原素去繼續吸取養份.  (呢個已經係對佢地最好既推論, 要諗衰 d 佢地金主係邊個, 點營運落去係從來無公開過)"},{"pid":"7a3210f668b6cd1185c2326777177d2948a52ad8","tid":1958784,"uid":188437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5439a62fadb4350fe231de23fb413499109a02ac","tid":1958784,"uid":11738,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T02:56:41.000Z","msg":"熱狗抗疫方面都好超然，個個唔戴口罩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:35:54.000Z","msg":"狗罩平過口罩,熱狗要慳返黎課金"},{"pid":"d1e1ff701f95847847d301920269a1ef187285e7","tid":1958784,"uid":253983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a7ad111f34bfaef6395b9d31b7848a3cb2a2a338","tid":1958784,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T02:46:39.000Z","msg":"就黎連牆紙都被批鬥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:47:01.000Z","msg":"批緊啦已經<br />\n逼到牆紙撤回篇文<br />\n<br />\n但事實係小弟唔覺得篇文關於熱<span style=\"color: red;\">普</span>城嘅描述有乜嘢錯<br />\n包括「反勇武抗爭」呢個point"},{"pid":"9b0a35bd071c830c7878f1c327eb0b6d72f70969","tid":1958784,"uid":136393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7ad111f34bfaef6395b9d31b7848a3cb2a2a338","tid":1958784,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T02:46:39.000Z","msg":"就黎連牆紙都被批鬥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:47:14.000Z","msg":"不如話係有人帶自己陣營串人地陣營啲私貨入去牆紙。"},{"pid":"49653b930aef0a8ed39e03660c1e34766079b7de","tid":1958784,"uid":169469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a7ad111f34bfaef6395b9d31b7848a3cb2a2a338","tid":1958784,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T02:46:39.000Z","msg":"就黎連牆紙都被批鬥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T04:13:08.000Z","msg":"批鬥緊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db2f992f994d06ac276a9ab29f99669d3a7ae53","tid":1958784,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T04:16:50.000Z","msg":"又要做雞<br />\n又要介意俾人話佢做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491df0b15d7f13df79b079e9253dbaeda608025b","tid":1958784,"uid":1241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T04:39:46.000Z","msg":"2020仲熱普城<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3599a17795f17fb25201c8300d48dbab5bea6c","tid":1958784,"uid":36702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"係咪當年篤數篤到播雪花都有幾千人收看嘅熱血時報？"},{"pid":"ed03324d4ae4b6b4ffcd53f89bb4eb2018c4f3fc","tid":1958784,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T04:41:13.000Z","msg":"乞嗤<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}